  width: ${props => 100 - props.theme.rightPanel.width}%;
  padding: ${props => props.theme.spacingUnit * 2}px;
 
  ${media.lessThan('medium')`
    width: 100%;
  `};
`;
 
export const RightPanel = styled.div`

  ${media.lessThan('medium')`

  `};
`;
 
export const DarkRightPanel = styled(RightPanel)`

  `};
